  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Nov 2022</code>: Our paper, <a href="https://sites.cs.ucsb.edu/~arpitgupta/pdfs/trustee.pdf">AI/ML for Network Security: The Emperor has no Clothes</a>, received the <strong>Best Paper Honorable Mention</strong> at ACM SIGSAC Conference on Computer and Communications Security (CCS), 2022. It was rated as the best paper in the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Machine Learning and Security</code> track. Special congratulations to <a href="https://maybe-hello-world.github.io/">Roman Beltiukov</a> and <a href="https://asjacobs92.github.io/">Arthur Jacobs</a>! 🏆</li>
